Let's split the super business license on two parts: the business license and the recurring license.
<br />

<br />
* The cost of the business license is the same, $29.95.
<br />
* The cost of the recurring license is $29.95 minus 30%.
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">2. And this license is for 500 downloads/domains?</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
