The business license is prerequisite and purchased only once. The recurring license is for 500 downloads/domains.
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">3. After 500 downloads/domains I have to purchase another license for the next 500? </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
Nearly yes. You have to purchase another <span style="font-style: italic">recurring</span> license <span style="font-style: italic">before</span> 500 downloads/domains.
<br />

<br />
Therefore, the initial minimal cost of the super business license is (I hope my calculator is good) $50.91 (one business plus one recurring).
